config MFD_SM5714
        bool "Siliconmitus SM5714 IFPM Support"
        depends on I2C=y
        select MFD_CORE
        help
          Say yes here to support for Siliconmitus SM5714.
          This is a Power Management IC with Single Flash, Charger, Type-C, MUIC, FG
          controls on chip.
          This driver provides common support for accessing the device;
          additional drivers

